
hi. Welcome to hoos.in!

hoos.in is a social network that makes it easy to live a creative, adventurous and generally awesome social life. 

How it Works

Check your social calendar on your home page to see what your friends are up to and to find creative ideas from your community for what you can do together.  

Click on an idea to see the details and who's going. You can join an existing idea or add your own idea to the mix- either way, pick who you want to share it with and invite them to join by clicking their face.


Find friends by searching their name or through Facebook in the header.

Most of all, join something fun and go do great things with friends!


Who are we?

hoos.in is a start-up based in Madison, WI with the mission to make it easy for everyone to do great things with friends. 
